Package: trac-ticketvalidemail
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, trac (>= 0.11)
Description: Only accept valid RFC822 e-mail addresses from anonymous reporters
 Extends Trac to only accept anonymous tickets when the reporter name is a
 valid RFC822 e-mail address.
